Requirements: 

The pattern starts with 1 and increments by 1 

Numbers divisible by 3 are replaced with “fizz” 

Numbers divisible by 5 are replaces with “buzz” 

Numbers divisible by 15 are replaces with “fizz buzz” 

Incorrect input (doesn’t match pattern or incorrect string) or longer than 5 seconds to respond from user ends the game 
 

Should be focused on running efficiently 

Design: 

Written in Python 

While loop for the core of program 

Checks divisibility for 15, 5, then 3 using if statements 

User inputs items one by one  
